---
title: Summery Chicken Thigh Salad with Green Onion Dressing
description: Get ready to feel the sunshine! Tonight's dinner is a pop of bright, summery flavours with a green onion dressing that clings to sweet snow peas, juicy chicken and crunchy cucumber. This meal is an instant pick-me-up!
